</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/DarkSeal" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/DarkSeal">Dark Seal</a></em> series (also known as <em>Gate of Doom</em> [first game] and <em>Wizard Fire</em> [second game])
</li><li> <em>Escape from the Planet of the Robot Monsters</em>
